=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex6 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright gritty sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 1274 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1273.5991
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.0965
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0412
  pitch_clarity: 14.3558
  inharmonicity: 0.4253
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -3.8674
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

